- @title = "CrossFit Box Name Generator"
= render :partial => 'layouts/top_nav', :locals => { :title => "CrossFit Name Generator" }
.col-md-12
  .well
    %p Using the #{ link_to 'Big Thesaurus API', 'http://words.bighugelabs.com/', :target => 'blank'}, I built the CrossFit name generator below.

    %p
      Simply input a "starting word" for your CrossFit box business name. Use words like
      %b angry, fierce, strong,
      etc.

    %p Click "Generate Names" and a list of possible CrossFit box names will be generated.

    %p The "CrossFit Name Generator" is a service of Boost Fitness Marketing, the creators of #{ link_to 'FitnessTexter', 'http://boostfitnessmarketing.com/fitnesstexter', :target => 'blank'}, the text message marketing service used by over 300 fitness businesses to increase their membership volume.

  %hr


  %hr
    .well
      %h5 How It Works
      %p
        1. Input word is sent to Big Thesaurus API via a Rails AJAX request using the 'net/http' library
        %br
        2. Big Thesaurus looks up word, and if it exists, it sends back a JSON file with synonyms, antonyms, etc
        %br
        3. JSON file is parsed for just the synonyms hash
        %br
        4. Hash is set as an instance variable
        %br
        5. Iterate over the instance variable of synonyms, prepending the word "CrossFit" to each.
  %hr

  .col-md-4
    .panel.panel-primary
      .panel.panel-heading
        %h3.panel-title CrossFit Name Generator
      .panel-body
        %p
          The name generator has been used:
          %b
            %span#crossfit-counter
              =@counter.count
              times
        %hr
        %p
          Please use singular adjectives such as:
          %b funny, crazy, powerful,
          etc.
        = form_tag crossfit_name_generator_index_path, action: "create", remote: "true" do
          .form-group
            .input-group
              .input-group-addon
                %span.glyphicon.glyphicon-arrow-right
              = text_field_tag :query, nil, :class => 'form-control', :placeholder => "Enter Search Term"
          = submit_tag('Generate Names', class:'btn btn-primary')
  .col-md-8
    .panel.panel-primary
      .panel.panel-heading
        %h3.panel-title Possible CrossFit Names
      .panel-body#crossfit-names{ :style => "text-align: center;"}
